      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "I guess sram is better...\nAnd I could structure a 6502 core to use a large amount of on die ram cache, and still use external address space. \n\nNot sure yet. I guess the ram makers have their own tricks",
